data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. This beautiful Triple Creek home has it all, high ceilings, a formal living room & dining or flex space and beautiful arches, a large family room, and an open kitchen. The kitchen features 42" staggered cabinets, granite countertops, a large island, upgraded stainless steel appliances, a large pantry, a breakfast bar, and a breakfast nook. Offering beautiful large ceramic tile in all living areas. One bedroom and bath are located downstairs, perfect for guests or in-laws. Upstairs you will find the spacious loft and large theater room, and 4 additional bedrooms and baths. The master suite features two walk-in closets, a large bathroom with a garden tub, a dual sink, a stand-up shower, and a private water closet. The entire home has brand-new exterior paint. Fully fenced with a huge backyard, perfect to add a pool! Located in Triple Creek which features amazing resort-style pools, a gym, playgrounds, walking trails, dog parks, and more!
